                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7309" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0283</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10146 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作业成本法：看不透的物流成本——J公司物流成本核算改革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Operation cost method: the invisible logistics cost- -J Company&#39;s logistics cost accounting reform road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘俊艳，张宇，王光玉，刘畅，周晓辉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛励卓智造工业科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作业成本法；物流成本；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Activity based costing;Logistics cost</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">J公司是一家外贸型家纺企业，利润薄，除原料成本外，物流成本是该企业一直重点关注的主要成本项；然而以经济批量概念为基础的传统标准成本制度，无法计算与产品无关的成本，从而失去了它存在的基础，导致产品成本失真。J公司对物流成本管理进行改革，采用作业成本法，将物流“作业”成本按作业动因分配到物流成本中，其重点并不在于成本的计算，而在于降低成本，加强成本管理。通过数据分析，标准成本法所得物流成本比基于作业成本法所得物流成本低11.2%，在作业成本下，以作业量为基础分配制造费用，使成本计算准确性提高；更让案例企业管理者将注意力集中在发生成本的原因——成本动因上，而不仅仅是关注成本结果，才能切实贯彻持续管理优化。本案例适用于《管理会计》、《企业管理》、《运营管理》、《精益生产》、《工业工程》等MBA、MEM专业硕士相关课程，帮助学员学习管理会计相关知识，帮助制造业企业掌握实现现场降本增效的理论方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> J company is a foreign trade home textile enterprise with low profit, and the logistics cost is the main cost item of the enterprise. However, the traditional standard cost system based on the economic batch concept cannot calculate the irrelevant cost, thus losing the basis of its existence and the distortion of product cost. J Company reforms the logistics cost management, adopts the operation cost method, and allocates the logistics &quot;operation&quot; cost to the logistics cost according to the operation motivation. The focus is not on the cost calculation, but to reduce the cost and strengthen the cost management. Through data analysis, the logistics cost obtained by the standard cost method is 11.2% lower than that based on the operation cost method. Under the operation cost, the manufacturing cost is allocated to improve the cost calculation accuracy, and the case managers focus on the causes of the cost —— The cost motivation, not only focus on the cost results, so as to implement the continuous management optimization. This case is applicable to MBA and MEM master courses in Management Accounting courses, Business Management, Business Management, Lean Production and Industrial Engineering, etc., to help students to learn management accounting knowledge and manufacturing enterprises to master the theoretical methods of on-site cost reduction and efficiency increas</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作业成本法定义及应用场景；作业成本法实施条件；成本动因的定义；作业成本法实施步骤；作业成本法的实施步骤</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
